      <title>伊朗哈梅内伊表示愿意改善与西方的关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/iran-s-khamenei-signals-openness-to-improving-ties-with-west</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗最高领导人表示，伊朗愿意缓解与西方的外交接触，暗示新总统领导下，伊朗可能会采取更为和解的态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/iran-s-khamenei-signals-openness-to-improving-ties-with-west</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 09:47:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列议会夏季休会，内塔尼亚胡的压力减少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/israel-hamas-war-parliamentary-recess-takes-heat-off-netanyahu</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列议会于周日休会三个月，为总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡提供一些国内喘息的机会，因为该国面临着对加沙战争的批评、提前举行选举的呼声以及真主党在戈兰高地发动的造成十几名年轻人死亡的毁灭性袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/israel-hamas-war-parliamentary-recess-takes-heat-off-netanyahu</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 09:06:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯在第一周就筹集了 2 亿美元以建立战争基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/harris-raises-200-million-in-first-week-to-build-up-war-chest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯自参加 2024 年总统大选以来的一周内筹集了 2 亿美元，凸显了民主党人对其新推定候选人的热情高涨，并有助于抵制共和党的闪电战，唐纳德·特朗普在金钱竞赛中领先。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/harris-raises-200-million-in-first-week-to-build-up-war-chest</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>超过一半的英国人感觉比五年前更穷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-28/more-than-half-of-people-feel-poorer-than-they-did-five-years-ago-survey-finds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[研究发现，超过一半（53%）的人现在感觉比五年前更贫穷。]]></description>
