    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚选举前改组高级部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/australia-reshuffles-senior-ministers-ahead-of-upcoming-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴尼斯 (Anthony Albanese) 自 2022 年上任以来首次进行重大内阁改组，对移民和住房等重要职位的领导层进行了调整，他正在为未来 10 个月内必须举行​​的激烈选举做准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/australia-reshuffles-senior-ministers-ahead-of-upcoming-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 05:56:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨未能推动德国经济起飞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/germany-economy-olaf-scholz-is-failing-to-engineer-a-liftoff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国无法实现有意义的增长，给其经济的长期前景和总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨领导下的三个执政党的政治希望蒙上了一层阴影。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/germany-economy-olaf-scholz-is-failing-to-engineer-a-liftoff</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾能源部称网站遭黑客攻击并被篡改</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/philippines-energy-department-says-website-was-hacked-defaced</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾能源部表示，正在调查周六其一个网站遭到黑客攻击的情况，并已下线该网站以修复系统漏洞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/philippines-energy-department-says-website-was-hacked-defaced</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 02:08:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国、日本、韩国希望在美国投票前巩固安全关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/us-japan-south-korea-look-to-cement-security-ties-before-america-votes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国承诺将全力保卫盟友日本和韩国，并与其签署协议，以在 11 月美国选出下一任总统之前巩固安全合作成果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/us-japan-south-korea-look-to-cement-security-ties-before-america-votes</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
